@AspireForge.ApiService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5236

### Health check
GET {{AspireForge.ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/hello
Accept: application/json

###

### Authenticated user info (requires Bearer token)
GET {{AspireForge.ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/me
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Admin dashboard (requires seacoast_owneradmin role)
GET {{AspireForge.ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/admin/dashboard
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List tenants
GET {{AspireForge.ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/admin/tenants
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
